text: Dominique McElligott (5 October 1986) is an Irish actress. She appears in mostly independent movies. She played Joy Dietz in Not Fade Away. She also played Emily in Dark Floors. McElligott was born in Dublin, Ireland. ==References== Category:Irish television actors Category:Irish movie actors Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Dublin
